b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2109,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!","message":"<div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurer starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1617774000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adventurer affected this time and his stats are described below.<\/div><div>Note: Unlocking a 5\\u2605 Gala Dragalia adventurer&#39;s mana spiral requires special materials specific to that adventurer that can be earned from the daily bonus of the Trials of the Mighty quest.<br><br><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Adventurers<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Prince (light\/sword)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Stats<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 adventurer<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp adjust\\">\\n<div class=\\"thumbList\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"thumbnail\\">\\n\\t\\t<img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/3bd19f2da8dbe54089e8b4d50e1530b32.png\\">\\n\\t\\t<img class=\\"rarity\\" src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/23b8fc2cd656aa0d5ef96984f257ce7e2.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"discription\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"charaName\\">Gala Prince<\/div><\/div>\\n<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5d54775020f2b8c24e8e1d445b58d2ad2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>908<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>602<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>3,210<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c8617d88f15afc0758a831a32f276e572.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Rising Circlet<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>7<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>and creates a buff zone that increases strength.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 1,700 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 3,817<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 16,794<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength +20%<br>\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br><\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/e3c8bf74f6e5d50e339f98d82b8411472.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Exalted Glory<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>inflicts paralysis, increases the entire team\'s<br>strength and defense, grants all teammates<br>a shield, and grants the user a strength amp.<br>The skill gauge for this skill can be filled by<br>attacking enemies, but it will also gradually<br>fill automatically.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 134 \\u00d7 3 hits<br>Damage: 400 \\u00d7 10 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: (Fills Automatically)<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength +15%<br>\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbDefense +20%<br>\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbShield<br>\\u3000Charges: 1<br>\\u3000Potency: 30% of max HP<br>\\u30fbParalysis<br>\\u3000Lasts 13 seconds<br>\\u3000Triggers every 3.9 seconds<br>\\u3000Damage: 80.3<br>Amps:<br>\\u30fbStrength Amp (Team Amp MAX Lv. = 3)<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2993ccd3f5c88b4fc376f81999404f672.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shapeshifting Boost VIII<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAdds 10% to the modifier applied to damage<br>when in dragon form, and extends shapeshift<br>time by 20%. Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/368330649dd4e9c07abc8582ae510ece2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Light) Shapeshift = HP Regen VI<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Light:<br>each shapeshift grants them an HP regen buff<br>for 20 seconds. Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/62ec54c3111dcff5d7c6fadf0c9e0ae92.png\\"><\/span><span>Dragonlight\'s Resolve III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces dragon gauge depletion over time by 40%,<br>and increases attack rate when shapeshifted by 10%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/89cfb88183671a67f82c3ae2993958d42.png\\"><\/span><span>Sacred Shield III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to poison and curses<br>by 100%. When the user is hit by an attack<br>that would have poisoned or cursed them,<br>their strength is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/de137cf7302f5717d1be863dbd4a45e62.png\\"><\/span><span>Draconic Charge III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Fills 50% of the user\'s dragon gauge when<br>their HP drops to 40% (once per quest).<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1617602400,"prev_article_id":"2096","next_article_id":"2111","image_path":"","update_time":1617589915}}}'